Content: ---------------MEMES---------------NLWelcome to MEMES! We are a friendly clan where you can meet new friends_ or find new enemies.NLNLAbout Us:NLWe are a small  clan hoping to grow. We want to be able to pull out the best of your potential and become better but also be able to communicate with new people!NLNLContent Creators:NLWe are looking for content creators for YouTube_ and Twitch to help us grow through social media and for them to make montages for the team members etc!NL—————————————————-NLGFX Designers:NLLooking for GFX Designers to create logos_ banners_ templates for the clan and team members!NL—————————————————NLTry-out staff:NLWe are looking for active people that are able to recruit and try them out for the clan daily! | 10+ years | Must have mic | Must be willing to help | Must speak english.NL—————————————————NLDM ME FOR MORE INFO
